00:14:10.767 --> 00:14:11.935 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI growls]

00:14:12.018 --> 00:14:15.230 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI grunting]

00:14:15.313 --> 00:14:17.565 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI] I see now.
