00:14:17.649 --> 00:14:19.984 position:50% align:center
The height makes things
tougher than before.

00:14:20.068 --> 00:14:23.530 position:50% align:center
All right. I'm really
starting to enjoy this!

00:14:25.198 --> 00:14:28.076 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI grunts]
Ah, crap! Where's my foothold?

00:14:28.159 --> 00:14:30.912 position:50% align:center
Okay, just take a second
and assess your surroundings.

00:14:30.995 --> 00:14:34.082 position:50% align:center
Sakurai! Just move
your other leg first.

00:14:34.165 --> 00:14:36.126 position:50% align:center
If you initiate with your
right foot instead,

00:14:36.209 --> 00:14:37.377 position:50% align:center
