00:15:00.108 --> 00:15:01.443 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI growls]

00:15:01.526 --> 00:15:04.112 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI] He's having so much fun,
my jabs don't faze him!

00:15:04.195 --> 00:15:07.032 position:50% align:center
