00:15:20.795 --> 00:15:23.173 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
I so can't do this.

00:15:23.256 --> 00:15:25.675 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
She looks like a chrysalis.

00:15:25.759 --> 00:15:28.303 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI] I'll just stay up
here forever, I guess.

00:15:28.386 --> 00:15:30.680 position:50% align:center
Can't go forward, can't go back.

00:15:30.764 --> 00:15:32.682 position:50% align:center
This is my life now.

00:15:32.766 --> 00:15:35.143 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
That's a weird way to pout.

00:15:35.226 --> 00:15:36.895 position:50% align:center
[INSTRUCTOR A]
I'll let you down with the rope.

00:15:36.978 --> 00:15:39.397 position:50% align:center
