00:16:17.852 --> 00:16:20.105 position:50% align:center
you can pick up
our dinner tonight.

00:16:20.188 --> 00:16:21.940 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
Why, you little...

00:16:35.662 --> 00:16:37.122 position:50% align:center
