Reminds me of a
cornered feral cat

00:17:17.203 --> 00:17:20.165 position:50% align:center
who's scared to trust humans.
Look at him! So cute!

00:17:20.248 --> 00:17:22.542 position:50% align:center
Typical. I mean,
this is the same guy

00:17:22.625 --> 00:17:26.129 position:50% align:center
