00:17:48.401 --> 00:17:49.861 position:50% align:center
[NARRATOR]
Solo karaoke!

00:17:49.944 --> 00:17:52.530 position:50% align:center
True to its name, the act
of singing in a room alone

00:17:52.614 --> 00:17:54.991 position:50% align:center
