in "party of one."

00:17:55.075 --> 00:17:56.326 position:50% align:center
It's an effective method

00:17:56.409 --> 00:17:57.827 position:50% align:center
for practicing
singing techniques

00:17:57.911 --> 00:18:00.413 position:50% align:center
without the pressure of an
audience judging and laughing.

00:18:00.497 --> 00:18:03.124 position:50% align:center
Its adherents are
growing in number.

00:18:03.208 --> 00:18:05.794 position:50% align:center
However! Traditionally,
karaoke has been considered

00:18:05.877 --> 00:18:08.755 position:50% align:center
