if you're spotted going solo,

00:18:08.838 --> 00:18:10.632 position:50% align:center
odds are you'll be
teased relentlessly

00:18:10.715 --> 00:18:12.300 position:50% align:center
at school or work
the following day.

00:18:12.384 --> 00:18:14.135 position:50% align:center
So, you'd better avoid
the water cooler!

00:18:14.219 --> 00:18:16.012 position:50% align:center
And watch out for
the receptionist!

00:18:16.096 --> 00:18:17.389 position:50% align:center
[RECEPTIONIST]
It's that sad boy.

00:18:17.472 --> 00:18:20.058 position:50% align:center
