tune in front of your friends--

00:18:24.979 --> 00:18:26.398 position:50% align:center
Compared to the embarrassment of

00:18:26.481 --> 00:18:28.900 position:50% align:center
bombing the rap section,
such treatment is nothing!

00:18:28.983 --> 00:18:31.736 position:50% align:center
In other words, anyone who
attempts solo karaoke

00:18:31.820 --> 00:18:34.614 position:50% align:center
