some privacy back.

00:19:06.771 --> 00:19:07.731 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
Thanks?

00:19:07.814 --> 00:19:09.733 position:50% align:center
[ASAI]
Sakurai!

00:19:09.816 --> 00:19:11.818 position:50% align:center
