00:19:21.578 --> 00:19:22.996 position:50% align:center
Yeah, it's fun!

00:19:23.079 --> 00:19:25.290 position:50% align:center
Here, have a little drink.

00:19:28.585 --> 00:19:31.004 position:50% align:center
