sure how to answer that.

00:20:11.961 --> 00:20:14.589 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI] Um, Ami, I don't know
about this costume.

00:20:14.673 --> 00:20:16.341 position:50% align:center
Oh, you're fine, just relax!

00:20:16.424 --> 00:20:20.679 position:50% align:center
